<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA71">
<l>naṉṟu piṇimūppuk kaiyakaṟṟi nāṉkūḻi</l>
<l>niṉṟu nilamuḻutu māṇṭālu – meṉṟum</l>
<l>viṭalāḻi neñcamē vēṇṭiṉēṉ kaṇṭā</l>
<l>yaṭalāḻi koṇṭāṉmāṭ ṭaṉpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though he has well abolished illness and old age</l>
<l>[and] steadily rules the whole earth through the four aeons, always</l>
<l>immerse yourself in letting go , heart. I wanted, see,</l>
<l>love from him who took the deadly discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
